Mrs. Nita Ambani at the historic launch of India’s first ever Olympic Values Education Programme (OVEP) in Odisha today.

With the launch of OVEP, the build-up to the prestigious IOC 2023 Session in Mumbai has begun.

#OVEPIndia

Watch @shikhardofficial talk about his leadership skills and how he takes all situations and junctures in his career with a positive outlook. He goes on to elaborate on how he feels about mentoring the younger generation at the @forbesindia Leadership Awards 2022

He also highlights how he has been working on his physical and mental fitness along with his game to be ready for selection for the T20 WC this year, starting with the IPL, also adding his desire to play the 2023 ODI WC

#RiseAsOne

IOC Member Mrs. Nita Ambani believes the IOC Session 2023 in Mumbai will ignite India’s Olympic quest, as the country aspires to be a sporting nation to be reckoned with at the global stage.

#IOCSessionMumbai2023 #StrongerTogether #RiseAsOne
